Om te installeren:
Opties -> extra's -> extensions -> rechtsboven developer mode aanzetten -> uitgepakte extensie laden -> het mapje met de code selecteren

To install:
Options -> More tools -> extensions -> Enable "Developer mode" in the right-top -> load unpacked extension -> select the folder containing the code

supported shortkeys:

ctrl + s -> Save your code
ctrl + shift + s -> Submit your code
ctrl | alt + r -> Run your tests
ctrl | alt + shift + r -> Run the specification tests
